ve our Website, analyze usage, and optimize our services. </li><li> To comply with legal requirements and protect our rights and interests. </li></ul><p><strong>4. Cookies and Similar Technologies</strong><br> Our Website uses cookies and similar technologies to store your preferences, analyze user behavior, and provide you with a personalized experience. For more information, please refer to our Cookie Policy. </p><p><strong>5. Data Sharing with Third Parties</strong><br> We only share your personal data with third parties in the following cases: </p><ul><li> When necessary to provide our services (e.g., using third parties to send newsletters). </li><li>When required by law or to comply with legal obligations.</li><li> When you have given your consent or explicitly agreed to such sharing. </li></ul><p><strong>6. Data Security</strong><br> We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. We use SSL encryption for the transmission of sensitive  data. </p><p><strong>7. Your Rights</strong><br> You have certain rights regarding your personal data, including the right to access, correct, delete, and restrict its processing. If you wish to exercise your rights or have any questions about the use of your data, please contact us using the contact details provided below. </p><p><strong>8. Changes to this Policy</strong><br> We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our  privacy practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any changes to this policy will be posted on this page, and the &quot;Effective Date&quot; at the top will be updated accordingly. </p>",11),id=l("strong",null,"9. Contact Us",-1),ld=l("br",null,null,-1),sd=l("br",null,null,-1),cd=l("br",null,null,-1),md=l("br",null,null,-1),ud=l("a",{class:"link-default",href:"tel:+4972316084047"},"+49 7231 6084047",-1),zd=l("br",null,null,-1),dd=["href"],_d={key:0,class:"h1_net"},pd={class:"text"},hd=l("p",{clas